{
  "stem": "25831.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we did get that visa for Canada.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that visa was issued to my mother, my father, and my grandfather, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] which was very good for my grandfather because he would have come under the Polish quota and he couldn't have come to America, to the United States.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Father.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his name is Conitzer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But coming back to that visa, after my father died, his Canadian visa became invalid because it wasn't as issued.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was issued to three people and now they were only two people who would come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that became invalid with Canadian visa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How was I notified?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got that cable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got a cable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On May 8, 1939.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got a cable which said [GERMAN], which means dad's seriously ill.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I called my mother in Breslau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said to her, when did he die, you know, knowing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she repeated again, he's very ill, very ill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I said again, when did he die?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then she said, today.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, how?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She said, she couldn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She didn't want to say it because the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was-- you know, all these conversations were monitored.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was afraid to say anything which might be provocative.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Have I told you already about the Gestapo visit to my house?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Gestapo came to our house in Breslau on May 8, 1939 to question my father about a contact he had made with an Englishman who is suspected of being a spy.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they came to the house, they said, please pack a bag.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We will take you in for questioning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was downtown doing shopping.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
